1) PdfRenderer has a deadlock somewhere inside its library. Unlikely.

2) Your file I/O is so complex, that writing multiple files in parallel simply takes 100 times longer. Remember the old Compact Disk (CD)? When reading one source you had full speed, as soon as 2+ processes read, it became exponentially slow (not HALF as fast, but rather 20 times slower for 2 processes). I think this is the most likely reason.

